{"ja393:0.1":"Jataka ","ja393:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja393:0.3":"Kharaputtavagga ","ja393:0.4":"8. Vighasadajataka ","ja393:1.1":"“Susukham vata jivanti, ","ja393:1.2":"ye jana vighasadino; ","ja393:1.3":"Dittheva dhamme pasamsa, ","ja393:1.4":"samparaye ca suggati”. ","ja393:2.1":"“Sukassa bhasamanassa, ","ja393:2.2":"na nisametha pandita; ","ja393:2.3":"Idam sunatha sodariya, ","ja393:2.4":"amhevayam pasamsati”. ","ja393:3.1":"“Naham tumhe pasamsami, ","ja393:3.2":"kunapada sunatha me; ","ja393:3.3":"Ucchitthabhojino tumhe, ","ja393:3.4":"na tumhe vighasadino”. ","ja393:4.1":"“Sattavassa pabbajita, ","ja393:4.2":"mejjharanne sikhandino; ","ja393:4.3":"Vighaseneva yapenta, ","ja393:4.4":"mayance bhoto garayha; ","ja393:4.5":"Ke nu bhoto pasamsiya”. ","ja393:5.1":"“Tumhe sihanam byagghanam, ","ja393:5.2":"valanancavasitthakam; ","ja393:5.3":"Ucchittheneva yapenta, ","ja393:5.4":"mannivho vighasadino. ","ja393:6.1":"Ye brahmanassa samanassa, ","ja393:6.2":"annassa va vanibbino; ","ja393:6.3":"Datvava sesam bhunjanti, ","ja393:6.4":"te jana vighasadino”ti. ","ja393:7.1":"Vighasadajatakam atthamam. "}